import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, 400)
y = np.sin(x ** 3)

fig, axs = plt.subplots(2)
axs[0].plot(x, y)
axs[1].plot(x, -y)

plt.show()
